Description: Contains the tutorials for the JADS course "Social Network Analysis for Data Science" (2021-2022). Update the package frequently, to have access to the most up-to-date tutorials. The tutorials will be added throughout the semester. The package contains a vignette that shows the most important functions you need to know for this course.
